#. type: Plain text
#: archlinux debian-buster debian-unstable mageia-cauldron
msgid "sm-notify - send reboot notifications to NFS peers"
msgstr "sm-notify - Envoyer une notification de redémarrage aux pairs NFS"

#. type: SH
#: archlinux debian-buster debian-unstable mageia-cauldron
